'''史蓋勒·奧斯丁·利普斯坦'''（Skylar Astin Lipstein，{{bd|1987年|9月23日}}），美國男演員以及歌手。為人所知的角色為《[[歌喉讚|歌喉讚]]》及《[[歌喉讚2|歌喉讚2]]》裡的「傑西·史旺森」。他亦是[[百老匯|百老匯]]音樂劇《{{link-en|春醒|Spring Awakening}}》的原班演員，也參與過電影《{{link-en|續寫哈姆雷特|Hamlet 2}}》、《[[胡士托風波|胡士托風波]]》、《{{link-en|Cavemen|Cavemen (film)}}》以及《[[21玩過界|21玩過界]]》。他也在《[[瘋狂前女友|瘋狂前女友]]》飾演「葛瑞格·塞拉諾」一角，該角色原演員為{{link-en|桑提諾·方塔納|Santino Fontana}}。他近期的演出作品為電視[[歌舞片|歌舞]][[喜劇|喜劇]]《[[佐伊的超凡歌单|佐伊的超凡歌单]]》，飾演麥斯（Max）一角。

==早期生活==
史蓋勒出生於[[紐約市|紐約市]]，並在[[羅克蘭縣_(紐約州)|紐約州羅克蘭縣]][[新城_(紐約州)|新城]]長大。其父親 Barry Lipstein 為服裝業主管，母親為 Meryl  Lipstein。<ref>Jackson, Brian Keith. "Broadways new teen heroes: Our own cast bios of the 'Spring Awakening' kids", ''[[New_York_(magazine)|New York]]'' '''40''' (9): 152–3.</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://archive.lohud.com/article/20130615/LIFESTYLE/306150106/Skylar-Astin-Barry-Lipstein |title=Archived copy |access-date=December 7, 2014 |url-status=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141213142657/http://archive.lohud.com/article/20130615/LIFESTYLE/306150106/Skylar-Astin-Barry-Lipstein |archive-date=2014-12-13 }}</ref> 他有一個姊妹 Brielle 以及兩個兄弟 Milan 與 Jace。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.lohud.com/article/20121002/ENTERTAINMENT/310020032/Tuesday-Q-Rockland-s-Skylar-Astin-gets-roll-Hollywood |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-10-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121004234444/http://www.lohud.com/article/20121002/ENTERTAINMENT/310020032/Tuesday-Q-Rockland-s-Skylar-Astin-gets-roll-Hollywood |archivedate=2012-10-04 }} was it supposed to be this? [http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/lohud/access/2775906291.html?FMT=CITE&date=Oct+02%2C+2012]{{dead link|date=February 2013 }}</ref> 史蓋勒是[[猶太人|猶太人]]。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.jewishexponent.com/article/16639/Summer_Awakening__for_Skylar_/|title=Summer Awakening for Skylar?|last=Elkin|first=Michael|date=July 17, 2008|publisher=''[[The_Jewish_Exponent|The Jewish Exponent]]''|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120601042210/http://www.jewishexponent.com/article/16639/Summer_Awakening__for_Skylar_/|archivedate=2012年6月1日|accessdate=August 18, 2013|deadurl=yes}}</ref> 在 {{link-en|Clarkstown High School North}} 高中畢業之後，他參加 {{link-en|Stagedoor Manor}} [[表演藝術|表演藝術]][[夏令營|夏令營]]。之後進入[[紐約大學|紐約大學]]的 {{link-en|Tisch School of the Arts}} 學校，然而當他參與《{{link-en|春醒|Spring Awakening}}》的演出時就休學了。<ref name="WSN1">{{cite news|url=http://www.nyunews.com/2.6087/putting-nyu-on-hold-for-broadway-1.637967|title=Putting NYU on hold for Broadway|last=Lapowsky|first=Issie|date=April 24, 2007|publisher=Washington Square News|pages=nyunews.com|accessdate=2009-05-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130130174353/http://www.nyunews.com/2.6087/putting-nyu-on-hold-for-broadway-1.637967|archivedate=2013-01-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/109174-PHOTO_CALL_New_Spring_Awakening_Billboard_Blooms_Outside_the_O%27Neill_Theatre|title=New Spring Awakening Billboard Blooms Outside the O'Neill Theatre|last=Kalafatus|first=Greg|date=June 27, 2007|work=playbill.com|publisher=[[Playbill|Playbill]]|accessdate=2009-05-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120910054532/http://www.playbill.com/news/article/109174-PHOTO_CALL_New_Spring_Awakening_Billboard_Blooms_Outside_the_O'Neill_Theatre|archivedate=2012-09-10}}</ref> 當他15歲的時候，他經紀人選擇他的中間名，當作史蓋勒的藝名。<ref name=mvoe1/>

==演藝生涯==
史蓋勒最後一次演出''Spring Awakening'' 是在2008年7月19日。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.goerie.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20080828/ENTERTAINMENT0702/808280331/-1/SHOWCASE|title=Steve Coogan and 'Hamlet 2' have their funny moments, but that's all they are -- moments.|last=Lemire|first=Christy|date=August 28, 2008|work=goerie.com|publisher=[[Erie_Times_News|Erie Times News]]|accessdate=2009-05-16|archive-date=2011-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110607014634/http://www.goerie.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20080828%2FENTERTAINMENT0702%2F808280331%2F-1%2FSHOWCASE|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="DV">{{cite news|url=http://www.accessmylibrary.com/coms2/summary_0286-15932962_ITM|title=Spring Awakening.(Off B'way)(Theater review)|last=Rooney|first=David|date=June 16, 2006|work=accessmylibrary.com|publisher=[[Daily_Variety|Daily Variety]]|accessdate=2009-05-16}}</ref><ref name="BC1">{{cite web|url=http://www.broadway.com/Past-Present-and-Future-Spring-Awakening-Stars-Say-Goodbye-and-Hello/broadway_photos/568907|title=Past , Present and Future ''Spring Awakening'' stars say hello and goodbye|date=July 19, 2008|work=broadway.com|accessdate=2009-05-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090115125917/http://www.broadway.com/Past-Present-and-Future-Spring-Awakening-Stars-Say-Goodbye-and-Hello/broadway_photos/568907|archivedate=2009-01-15}}</ref>

史蓋勒曾經在2010年8月6日~8日於[[好萊塢露天劇場|好萊塢露天劇場]]飾演[[吉屋出租|吉屋出租]]當中的 Mark Cohen 的角色，當時的導演為[[尼爾·柏德烈·夏里斯|尼爾·柏德烈·夏里斯]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.broadwayworld.com/article/Brady_Tveit_Astin_And_Thoms_To_Lead_RENT_At_Hollywood_Bowl_20100430 |title=Brady, Tveit, Astin And Thoms Join RENT At Hollywood Bowl<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-01-05 |archive-date=2012-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120112211135/http://broadwayworld.com/article/Brady_Tveit_Astin_And_Thoms_To_Lead_RENT_At_Hollywood_Bowl_20100430 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

史蓋勒曾飾演電影[[續寫哈姆雷特|續寫哈姆雷特]](Hamlet 2)當中的 Rand Posin 。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mlive.com/movies/index.ssf/2008/08/hamlet_2_hey_kids_lets_put_on.html|title='Hamlet 2': Hey, kids! Let's put on an offensive show!|last=Sanford|first=James|date=August 27, 2008|work=mlive.com|publisher=[[Kalamazoo_Gazette|Kalamazoo Gazette]]|accessdate=2009-05-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081122133145/http://www.mlive.com/movies/index.ssf/2008/08/hamlet_2_hey_kids_lets_put_on.html|archivedate=2008-11-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=CSTB&p_theme=cstb&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=122B9FB928613438&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM|title=All Shakespeare needed was a gay men's chorus|last=Ebert|first=Roger|date=August 22, 2008|work=newsbank.com|publisher=[[Chicago_Sun-Times|Chicago Sun-Times]]|accessdate=2009-05-16|archive-date=2012-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121019002721/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=CSTB&p_theme=cstb&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=122B9FB928613438&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM|dead-url=no}}</ref> 並與戲中的主要演員[[Phoebe_Strole|Phoebe Strole]]一同演唱電影原聲帶的歌曲「"Raped in the Face"」，該電影的主角為[[Steve_Coogan|Steve Coogan]]。由於該部電影在2008年的[[日舞影展|日舞影展]]上上映，這使得史蓋勒得以與美國的經紀公司[[United_Talent_Agency|United Talent Agency]]簽約。<ref>Goldstein, Gregg; and Simmons, Leslie (February 7, 2008). "Seems Sundance did have deals", ''[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]'' '''403''': 3–4.</ref>

史蓋勒之後在2009年曾為CBS電視台的情境喜劇''Ace in the Hole''的角色成員，但最終並未製作。<ref>Andreeva, Nellie (March 30, 2009). "Big Three cast leads on comedy", ''[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]'' '''409''': 4.</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.serienjunkies.de/news/ace-the-21645.html|title=Ace in the Hole: Pamela Adlon mit Hauptrolle ( Ace in the Hole: Pamela Adlon, with lead role)|last=Krannich|first=Michael|date=April 27, 2009|work=serienjunkies.de|publisher=Series Junkies|language=de|accessdate=2009-05-16|archive-date=2009-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090430115414/http://www.serienjunkies.de/news/ace-the-21645.html|dead-url=no}}([http://translate.google.com/translate?js=n&prev=_t&hl=en&ie=UTF-8&u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.serienjunkies.de%2Fnews%2Face-the-21645.html&sl=de&tl=en&history_state0= Google translation] {{Wayback|url=http://translate.google.com/translate?js=n&prev=_t&hl=en&ie=UTF-8&u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.serienjunkies.de%2Fnews%2Face-the-21645.html&sl=de&tl=en&history_state0= |date=20121108121842 }})</ref> 到了2010年，他也成為Fox電視台的情境喜劇 ''Strange Brew''的一員，最終也並未製作。

史蓋勒在2011年7月以客串演出的形式在影集[[Love_Bites_(TV_series)|Love Bites]]當中現身，並且在2012年5月客串演出[[女孩我最大|女孩我最大]]。他同時在2012年5月間於[[怪醫豪斯|怪醫豪斯]]第八季客串演出。

在2012年的時候，史蓋勒主演一部喜劇電影[[歌喉讚|歌喉讚]]，飾演 Jesse Swanson ，之後在2013年主演喜劇電影[[21玩過界|21玩過界]]飾演 Casey。

他在TBS電視台的情境喜劇[[愛情零距離|愛情零距離]]當中飾演男主角布洛迪(Brody Moyer)，一位年輕的投資經紀人愛上了位在同一棟大樓底層的女孩。

